<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6319] ReplicationSource can call terminate on itself and deadlock</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6319</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In a few places in the ReplicationSource code calls terminate on itself which is a problem since in terminate() we wait on that thread to die.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12597340">HBASE-6319</key>
            <summary>ReplicationSource can call terminate on itself and deadlock</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">Bug</type>
